text: Burangulovo () is a rural locality (a village) in Mansurovsky Selsoviet, Uchalinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 67 as of 2010. There are 3 streets. == Geography == It is located 45 km from Uchaly. == References == Category:Rural localities in Uchalinsky District
title: Burangulovo, Uchalinsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
